title: Irakli Toçi
text: Irakli Toçi (born 30 June 1981) is an <a href="Albania">Albania</a>n retired <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who played for <a href="KS%20Gramozi%20Ersek%C3%AB">KS Gramozi Ersekë</a>, <a href="KS%20Luft%C3%ABtari%20Gjirokast%C3%ABr">KS Luftëtari Gjirokastër</a> and <a href="KF%20Elbasani">KF Elbasani</a> in the Albanian Superliga.
